
Math-o-mir is a free mathematical notepad software. It is similar to Mathcad, although intended to write down more informal mathematical text and notes.
List of functions and features:
* Equation editing using keyboard and/or mouse
* Hand-drawings
* Text boxes
* Drawing boxes for more technical drawings
* Function plotting
* Basic symbolic computation
* Exporting raster images as .PNG, .JPG, .BMP
* Exporting MathML or LaTeX code (presentation MathML only)

